<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>《夏日草原》</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>文/苏坛</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">八月的草原</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是明眸里的一片绿海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">远山是一座岛屿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一棵棵树是奇异的风帆</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>飘荡起绿色的清流</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>我寻觅草海中泛起的色彩</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>雏菊开的纯洁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>萨日朗似火如焰</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或许这是美丽珊瑚的变幻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也可能是繁星坠入绿海</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">游牧在家乡的草原</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">我怎么能不心潮澎湃</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200801/ce99ecb8917e4838a81846659091cddc.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
